column5: Non-toxic goiter, also known as non-toxic goiter, nodule-thyroid, non tox, goiter, non-toxic, non-toxic goiter, non-toxic simple goiter, non-toxic simple goitre, nontoxic goiter, euthyroid goiter, and euthyroid goitre, is a type of goiter that is characterized by the sporadic enlargement of the thyroid gland without any changes in thyroid function or malignancy.
